text: is a former Japanese football player. She played for the Japan national team. ==Biography== Nakade was born in Mie Prefecture on December 6, 1988. After graduating from Kibi International University, she played for her local club Iga FC Kunoichi. In November 2008, Nakade was selected the Japan U-20 national team for 2008 U-20 World Cup. On September 26, 2013, she debuted for the Japan national team against Nigeria. ==Statistics== List of match in 2013 at Japan Football Association Japan national team Year Apps Goals 2013 1 0 Total 1 0 ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Footballers from Mie Prefecture Category:Japan women's international footballers Category:Nadeshiko League players Category:Iga FC Kunoichi Mie players
